entries.femaleVariant: This situation? Putrid, headed for a crash. Bubble's gonna burst, spew pus all over, tellin' ya.
I look around, I see their villas, their cars, their cocksucking poodles – I would drop napalm on it all.
They'll do the droppin', don't you worry. Longer they don't give a shit about peeps like us, the harder that social justice fist's gonna ream 'em come time.
Heh, yes, but the time must come first.
It will, don't worry. Justice is the ocean – ebb 'n' flow, ebb 'n' flow. North Oak's been livin' large at our expense for a while.
But the tide is risin', baby. An' you an' me are hangin' ten on the crest, my friend.
